{"id": "1218629255496335461", "channel_id": "1218629255496335461", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "旺达的支線地圖。\n◆◆◆⚠️注意◆◆◆\n當經過毒地板時（地圖中為紫色格子），會扣除自身 血量上限的 約5% 的血量，也就是固定值。\n經過該紫色地板時，若當前生命 低於 被扣除的血量，則會被判定為受到 致命傷害，並觸發相關效果（如死亡抵抗、復活確認）。\nuid100001547", "timestamp": "2024-03-16T18:37:35.547000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1218629255978553384", "filename": "Image_1710613973418.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1576670, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1218629255496335461/1218629255978553384/Image_1710613973418.jpg?ex=69cc146f&is=69cac2ef&hm=13991e180f4bdb3996bc4c3a2c8b6f83ba11973d613bfed18db2eb6bc1f29363&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1218629255496335461", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【意識潛遊】旺达「燃烧的群宴」地圖", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1211882178007408651"]}
